i was in the Chinatown area with my friends we couldn't decide what we want to eat  we were looking for something different  to eat. we came across empress garden  when we walk in the waitress was very nice first the waitress ask us what we want to drink i could decide she recommend us to try there mango smoothie told her sure i try it omg it so good she make it just right not to sweet and there ice coffee is  good too than we order Indonesia curry chicken and indonesia coconut shrimp OMG is so delicious than i when back couple time.oh forget to mention is BYOB, u could bring your own bottle.  highly recommend to everyone to try this restaurants.
